'''[[麥可·傑克森|麥可·傑克森]]的追思会'''于2009年7月7日在洛杉矶[[斯台普斯中心|斯台普斯中心]]举行，在此之前，杰克逊的私人悼念仪式在{{link-en|森林草坪纪念公园的自由大厅|Forest_Lawn_Memorial_Park_(Hollywood_Hills)#Court_of_Liberty}}举行。160万名歌迷在两天的申请期内申请了门票，由于参与人数之多，主办方采用了彩票式的方法最终以随机抽取了8,750人，每人得到两张门票。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.today.com/id/31710570/ns/today-entertainment/t/over-m-apply-jackson-memorial-tickets |title=Over 1.6M apply for Jackson memorial tickets |publisher=TODAY.com |agency=Associated Press |date=July 4, 2009 |accessdate=March 16, 2013 |archive-date=2016-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161119030902/http://www.today.com/id/31710570/ns/today-entertainment/t/over-m-apply-jackson-memorial-tickets |dead-url=no }}</ref>杰克逊的灵柩出现在追思会现场，但没有关于遗体最终处置的消息发布。杰克逊的追思会是网路媒体历史上观看人数最多的事件之一。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/TECH/07/07/michael.jackson.web.traffic/ |title=Michael Jackson memorial draws crowds online |publisher=CNN |accessdate=June 11, 2012 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234710/http://edition.cnn.com/2009/TECH/07/07/michael.jackson.web.traffic/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>据尼尔森估算，大约有3,310万美国人观看了追思会，相比较，2004年前总统{{link-en|罗纳德·里根下葬|Death and state funeral of Ronald Reagan}}大约有3,510万人收看，1997年[[戴安娜王妃的葬礼|戴安娜王妃的葬礼]]大约有3,310万美国人收看。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aoltv.com/insidetv/2009/07/09/michael-jackson-memorial-earns-31-million-viewers/ |title=Michael Jackson Memorial Earns 31 Million Viewers & More TV News |publisher=Aoltv.com |date=July 9, 2009 |accessdate=June 11, 2012 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723074833/http://www.aoltv.com/insidetv/2009/07/09/michael-jackson-memorial-earns-31-million-viewers/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

[[玛丽亚·凯莉|玛丽亚·凯莉]]、[[史提夫·汪达|史提夫·汪达]]、[[莱昂纳尔·里奇|莱昂纳尔·里奇]]、[[约翰·梅尔|约翰·梅尔]]、[[珍妮佛·哈德遜|珍妮弗·赫德森]]、[[亚瑟小子|亚瑟小子]]、[[杰梅因·杰克逊|杰梅因·杰克逊]]以及{{link-en|夏恩·贾法戈利|Shaheen Jafargholi}}上场表演。{{link-en|伯瑞·高迪|Berry Gordy}}和{{link-en|斯莫基·罗宾逊|Smokey Robinson}}献上了颂词，[[拉蒂法女皇|奎恩·拉提法]]朗读了由[[马娅·安杰卢|马娅·安杰卢]]为杰克逊写的诗《我们曾拥有他》（We had him）。[[艾尔·夏普顿|艾尔·夏普顿]]牧师告诉杰克逊的孩子“你们的父亲不是怪物，你们的父亲被迫对付的那些东西才是怪物。但是他不得不对付”时，赢得了全场的起立鼓掌和欢呼。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www2.macleans.ca/2009/07/07/there-was-nothing-strange-about-your-daddy|title=Video of Sharpton's eulogy|work=Macleans|date=July 7, 2009|publisher=macleans.ca|access-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209153325/http://www2.macleans.ca/2009/07/07/there-was-nothing-strange-about-your-daddy/|archive-date=2014-02-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>追思会最让人难忘的是杰克逊11岁的女儿帕丽斯·凯瑟琳首次公开发言，她哭着说出“从我出生以来，爸爸一直就是你所能想象出的最好的父亲……我只想说我爱他……那么的爱他。”<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/blog/2009/jul/07/michaeljackson | title=Liveblogging Michael Jackson's funeral and memorial service | work=The Guardian | date=July 7, 2009 | location=London | first=Oliver | last=Burkeman | accessdate=May 12, 2010 | archive-date=2013-07-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724004211/http://www.guardian.co.uk/news/blog/2009/jul/07/michaeljackson | dead-url=no }}</ref>西奥斯·史密斯牧师做出了最后的祈祷。<ref name="radiolive">{{cite web |url=http://www.radiolive.co.nz/Rev-Lucious-Smith-on-conducting-the-memorial-service-for-Michael-Jackson/tabid/506/articleID/14351/Default.aspx |title=Rev Lucious Smith on conducting the memorial service for Michael Jackson |publisher=Radio Live |date=June 28, 2010 |accessdate=March 16, 2013 |archive-date=2017-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510140323/http://www.radiolive.co.nz/Rev-Lucious-Smith-on-conducting-the-memorial-service-for-Michael-Jackson/tabid/506/articleID/14351/Default.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

杰克逊于2009年9月3日在加州[[格倫代爾_(加利福尼亞州)|格伦代尔]]的{{link-en|森林草坪纪念公园|Forest Lawn Memorial Park, Glendale}}下葬。<ref name="Michael Jackson finally laid to rest in Los Angeles">{{Cite news | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/michael-jackson/6136376/Michael-Jackson-finally-laid-to-rest-in-Los-Angeles.html | title=Michael Jackson finally laid to rest in Los Angeles | accessdate=September 8, 2009 | work=The Daily Telegraph | location=London | date=September 4, 2009 | first=Mark | last=Coleman | archive-date=2021-05-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508223400/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/michael-jackson/6136376/Michael-Jackson-finally-laid-to-rest-in-Los-Angeles.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

